msgstr "**Vettore lineare in ingresso**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1665
msgid "**Minimum distance between points (per feature)**"
msgstr "**Distanza minima tra i punti (per elemento)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1672
msgid "The minimum distance between points within one line feature"
msgstr "La distanza minima tra i punti all'interno di un elemento lineare"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1673
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1744
msgid "**Random points on lines**"
msgstr "**Punti casuali sulle linee**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1724
msgid "**Include line attributes**"
msgstr "**Includere gli attributi della linea**."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1725
msgid "``INCLUDE_LINE_ATTRIBUTES``"
msgstr "``INCLUDE_LINE_ATTRIBUTES``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1753
msgid "``LINES_WITH_MISSED_POINTS``"
msgstr "``LINES_WITH_MISSED_POINTS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1757
msgid "``POINTS_GENERATED``"
msgstr "``POINTS_GENERATED``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1769
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:randompointsonlines``"
msgstr "**ID Algoritmo**: ``native:randompointsonlines``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1779
msgid "Raster pixels to points"
msgstr "Da pixel raster a punti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1780
msgid ""
"Creates a vector layer of points corresponding to each pixel in a raster "
"layer."
msgstr ""
"Crea un layer vettoriale di punti corrispondenti ad ogni pixel di un layer "
"raster."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1783
msgid ""
"Converts a raster layer to a vector layer, by creating point features for "
"each individual pixel's center in the raster layer. Any NoData  pixels are "
"skipped in the output."
msgstr ""
"Converte un layer raster in un layer vettoriale, creando elementi puntuali "
"per il centro di ogni singolo pixel nel layer raster. I pixel NoData vengono"
" ignorati nel risultato."

